'''戴維·喬納森·舒爾金'''（{{lang-en|David Jonathon Shulkin}}；{{bd|1959年|6月22日|}}），曾任[[美國退伍軍人事務部|美國退伍軍人事務部]]部長。

== 簡介 ==
2015年3月18日，獲時任[[美國總統|美國總統]][[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]提名出任{{le|美國退伍軍人事務部健康次長|Under Secretary of Veterans Affairs for Health|退伍軍人部健康次長}}，2015年7月6日宣誓就職。

2017年1月11日，[[美國總統|美國總統]][[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]提名舒爾金出任[[美国退伍军人事务部长|美国退伍军人事务部长]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2017/01/11/509318144/trump-announces-david-shulkin-as-pick-for-secretary-of-veterans-affairs?utm_source=npr_newsletter&utm_medium=email&utm_content=20170111&utm_campaign=breakingnews&utm_term=nprnews |title=Domonoske, C. Trump Announces David Shulkin As Pick For Secretary Of Veterans Affairs, January 11, 2017, 11:44 AM ET |access-date=2017-01-21 |archive-date=2017-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170303080326/http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2017/01/11/509318144/trump-announces-david-shulkin-as-pick-for-secretary-of-veterans-affairs?utm_source=npr_newsletter&utm_medium=email&utm_content=20170111&utm_campaign=breakingnews&utm_term=nprnews |dead-url=no }}</ref>，隨後他辭去了私營部門工作以準備擔任此公職<ref>[http://newyork.cbslocal.com/2017/01/11/david-shuklin-trump-veterans-affairs/?e=i**N0bKsEQGlSg Who Is David Shulkin? 4 Things To Know About Trump’s Latest Appointment] {{Wayback|url=http://newyork.cbslocal.com/2017/01/11/david-shuklin-trump-veterans-affairs/?e=i**N0bKsEQGlSg |date=20170113151719 }} [[CBS|CBS]] January 11, 2017</ref><ref>Lisa Rein, [https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/powerpost/wp/2017/01/11/david-shulkin-tapped-as-trumps-va-secretary/?utm_term=.3077fafce003 David Shulkin tapped as Trump’s VA secretary] {{Wayback|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/powerpost/wp/2017/01/11/david-shulkin-tapped-as-trumps-va-secretary/?utm_term=.3077fafce003 |date=20170315134506 }} [[washingtonpost.com|washingtonpost.com]] January 11, 2017</ref><ref>Camila Domonoske, [http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2017/01/11/509318144/trump-announces-david-shulkin-as-pick-for-secretary-of-veterans-affairs Trump Announces David Shulkin As Pick For Secretary Of Veterans Affairs] {{Wayback|url=http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2017/01/11/509318144/trump-announces-david-shulkin-as-pick-for-secretary-of-veterans-affairs |date=20201004081728 }} 